org.eclipse.incquery.tooling.core.generator.fragments

Interface IGenerationFragmentProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtensionBasedGenerationFragmentProvider

    public interface IGenerationFragmentProvider
    An interface for collecting code generation fragments for specific patterns. The concrete value is injected using the GeneratorModule-based injectors.
    Author:
    Zoltan Ujhelyi
